OL,3,CMidwife recruitment 'crisis' as
OL,4,Ctrainees say they can't afford to study
OL,6,FTrainee midwives are being forced to
OL,7,Fleave the profession because of
OL,8,F"immense financial pressures",
OL,9,Faccording to a Royal College of
OL,10,FMidwives (RCM) report.
OL,12,FThe report says clinical placements
OL,13,Fand longer term times mean students
OL,14,Fcannot take on additional work to
OL,15,Fsupplement their finances.
