OL,3,CMidwife recruitment 'crisis' as
OL,4,Ctrainees say they can't afford to study
OL,6,FFiona Gibb, Director of Professional
OL,7,FMidwifery at the RCM, said student
OL,8,Fmidwives' options are to "take on paid
OL,9,Fwork on top of their heavy study and
OL,10,Fplacement schedule, to take on more
OL,11,Fdebt, including borrowing from family
OL,12,Fand friends, or to drop out and leave
OL,13,Ftheir dreams of becoming a midwife
OL,14,Fbehind them".
OL,16,FThe union is calling on the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment to offer better financial
OL,18,Fsupport to people studying to become
OL,19,Fmidwives.
