OL,3,CMidwife recruitment 'crisis' as
OL,4,Ctrainees say they can't afford to study
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says is is again
OL,7,Fextending the NHS Bursary for eligible
OL,8,Fstudents this academic year and has
OL,9,F"maintained investment in education
OL,10,Fand training for the NHS workforce at
OL,11,F#281m this year".
OL,13,FDescribed as an "unreported crisis",
OL,14,Fthe RCM is calling for the government
OL,15,Fto commit to support that is in line
OL,16,Fwith inflation and reimbursement for
OL,17,Fthe cost of student placements.
OL,19,FWithout increased support, the RCM has
OL,20,Fwarned that the number of qualified
OL,21,Fmidwives will fall.
