OL,3,CMidwife recruitment 'crisis' as
OL,4,Ctrainees say they can't afford to study
OL,6,F"The system has to be smarter than
OL,7,Fthis, so that we don't lose these
OL,8,Ffuture midwives from an NHS that
OL,9,Fdesperately needs them", said Fiona
OL,10,FGibb.
OL,12,FStudent midwives with a permanent home
OL,13,Faddress in Wales can claim a non-
OL,14,Frepayable bursary, if they work in the
OL,15,Fcountry for two years after qualifying.
