OL,3,CMidwife recruitment 'crisis' as
OL,4,Ctrainees say they can't afford to study
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said, "We are
OL,7,Fonce again extending the NHS Bursary
OL,8,Ffor eligible healthcare students
OL,9,Fstudying in the 2024-25 academic year,
OL,10,Falongside removing the Reduced Rate of
OL,11,FMaintenance Loan for new and existing
OL,12,Feligible, full-time, Welsh-domiciled
OL,13,FNHS Wales Bursary students."
OL,15,FAdding, it has "maintained investment
OL,16,Fin education and training for the NHS
OL,17,Fworkforce at #281m this year".
